-T%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF-h%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-VIJVy8Y0ANVr-0aI1GXk9w">Toạ trung văn “Tư đế hương” hữu cảm - 坐中聞思帝鄉有感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%87nh-H%E1%BB%93-S%E1%BB%9F/author-mH2tWe7RQ4SVhKlHTfKyoQ">Lệnh Hồ Sở</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%B4ng-V%C5%A9-sinh-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-VDPbM6HbzyGfnLNl6bn0NQ">Tông Vũ sinh nhật - 宗武生日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-An-thu-d%E1%BA%A1/poem-0m79UnLoLs9k3aOYTJPKYg">Trường An thu dạ - 長安秋夜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-H%E1%BA%A1c-Ni%C3%AAn/V%C4%83n-nh%E1%BA%A1n/poem-a_OrKdptrEYJpbvU9cLhUQ">Văn nhạn - 聞雁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-H%E1%BA%A1c-Ni%C3%AAn/author-6o5MEWm8-MGYLu0WTNeA4Q">Đinh Hạc Niên</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
